videos.description: Jabari Parker loses Nicolas Batum on the post, takes one dribble to the rack and rises up to flush the two-handed slam on Marvin Williams.

videos.description: Kemba Walker slices through the paint, fends off Wendell Carter Jr. and kisses glass on the leaning and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Kemba cans off-balanced and-1

videos.description: Kemba Walker goes isolation on Cameron Payne, as he steps back and drains a nasty 3-pointer to close the half.

videos.description: Tony Parker drives baseline, drops the rock to Miles Bridges, who raises up and destroys the rim on a two-handed slam.

videos.description: Kemba Walker stuffed the stat sheet with 30 points on 11-of-18 shooting, canning 5 3's and chipping in 7 assists and 6 rebounds in the Hornets' 135-106 win.
